lead_paragraph: The Texas Rangers made a surprise run to the AL West Division title last season but their 2016 title hopes may rest on the ability of ace starter Yu Darvish to bounce back from elbow surgery.

headline.print_headline: Rangers Shot at AL West Title Rests on Darvish Return
